OL,3,GEast
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA cloudy start with a few light
OL,6,Fshowers. Some bright or occasional
OL,7,Fsunny spells developing. Further
OL,8,Fshowers breaking out into the
OL,9,Fafternoon, before easing by the
OL,10,Fevening. Breezy along the coast.
OL,11,FFeeling rather cool.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FAny showers fading to leave a
OL,14,Fdry night, with variable cloud and
OL,15,Fsome lengthy clear spells. Turning
OL,16,Flocally chilly, with some patchy fog
OL,17,Fand rural frost forming. Light winds.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
