OL,3,GEast
OL,4,
OL,5,CFriday:FAfter a chilly start, cloud
OL,6,Fwill increase from the south to bring
OL,7,Fsome outbreaks of showery rain during
OL,8,Fthe morning. Showers, locally heavy,
OL,9,Fbecoming more widespread in the
OL,10,Fafternoon.
OL,11,
OL,12,COutlook for Saturday to Monday:FFine
OL,13,Fand dry with warm sunny spells
OL,14,FSaturday. A narrow band of rain moves
OL,15,Fsouth on Sunday, with brighter skies
OL,16,Ffollowing. A few showers Monday. Often
OL,17,Fbreezy and feeling cooler.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
